<p>Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: "inline-block text-white bg-pink-700 hover:bg-pink-800 focus:ring-4 focus:ring-pink-300 font-medium rounded-lg
                        text-sm px-5 py-2.5 my-3 dark:bg-pink-600 dark:hover:bg-pink-700 focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-pink-800" %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
